  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "`Compiler`: parameter changes and new functions added (still to be defined)\r\n\r\n`Editor`: `monaco` like API\r\n\r\n`FileManager`: node.js like API\r\n\r\n`Network`: for the moment deprecated, might come back in a new version for having a high level of communication with the blockchain.\r\n\r\n`Provider`: a plugin which implement only `sendAsync`. In the plugin side we need a wrapper in order to use it with web3 or ethers (the wrapper basically has one method `sendAsync` which call the targeted plugin).\r\n\r\n`Storage`: still to be defined\r\n\r\n`Theme`: no change\r\n\r\n`Udapp`: for the moment deprecated, might come back in a new version for having a high level of communication with the blockchain.\r\n\r\n`Wallet`: Same as `Provider` but implementing only account related rpc methods.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n",
